						<div class="postbody">I don't know, but maybe it's because a 6502 is not capable of reading data directly from an SD card in real time.
<br />
<br />A homebrew cart could possibly load ROM info from an SD card and store it into RAM (and subsequently write-protect that RAM), but this would be significantly more difficult than just using Flash ROMs in the first place.</div>

					
